                  "id": "CnFFo",
                  "fill": "#444444",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Instead of replacing letters with fixed codes, Arithmetic Coding represents the entire message as a single, highly precise fractional number between 0 and 1. It operates by repeatedly zooming into a number line.",
