                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "As the algorithm encounters 'A' followed by 'B', it outputs the code for 'A' and adds the sequence 'AB' to its dictionary (Code 256). When it encounters 'AB' again later, it can output the single integer 256 instead of two separate characters.",
